{"schemaVersion":2,"book":"NAM","chapters":{"1":{"1":{"text":"Carga de Nínive. Libro de la visión de Nahúm de Elcos.","segments":[{"text":"Carga"},{"text":"de"},{"text":"Nínive.","strong":"H5210","morph":"NPCSFN"},{"text":"Libro","strong":"H5612","morph":"NCcSMC"},{"text":"de"},{"text":"la"},{"text":"visión","strong":"H2377","morph":"NCcSMC"},{"text":"de"},{"text":"Nahúm","strong":"H5151","morph":"NPHSMN"},{"text":"de"},{"text":"Elcos.","strong":"H512","morph":"NCESMNH"}],"strongs":["H2377","H512","H5151","H5210","H5612"]},"2":{"text":"Dios celoso y vengador es Jehová; vengador es Jehová, y Señor de ira; Jehová, que se venga de sus adversarios, y guarda enojo para sus enemigos.","segments":[{"text":"Dios","strong":"H410","morph":"NPDSMN"},{"text":"celoso","strong":"H7072","morph":"NCJSMN"},{"text":"y"},{"text":"vengador","strong":"H5358","morph":"VqAtSM-N"},{"text":"es"},{"text":"Jehová;","strong":"H3069","morph":"NPDSMN"},{"text":"vengador"},{"text":"es"},{"text":"Jehová,"},{"text":"y"},{"text":"Señor"},{"text":"de"},{"text":"ira;"},{"text":"Jehová,"},{"text":"que"},{"text":"se"},{"text":"venga","strong":"H5358","morph":"VqAtSM-N"},{"text":"de"},{"text":"sus","strong":"H1931","morph":"RBSM3"},{"text":"adversarios,","strong":"H6862","morph":"NCcPMS"},{"text":"y"},{"text":"guarda"},{"text":"enojo","strong":"H5201","morph":"VqAvSM-N"},{"text":"para"},{"text":"sus","strong":"H1931","morph":"RBSM3"},{"text":"enemigos.","strong":"H341","morph":"VqAtPM-S"}],"strongs":["H1931","H3069","H341","H410","H5201","H5358","H6862","H7072"]},"3":{"text":"Jehová es lento para la ira, y grande en poder, no tendrá por inocente al culpable. Jehová marcha en la tempestad y el torbellino, y las nubes son el polvo de sus pies.","segments":[{"text":"Jehová","strong":"H3068","morph":"NPDSMN"},{"text":"es"},{"text":"lento"},{"text":"para"},{"text":"la"},{"text":"ira,","strong":"H639","morph":"NCcDMN"},{"text":"y"},{"text":"grande"},{"text":"en"},{"text":"poder,"},{"text":"no","strong":"H3808"